ed";s:17:"recorddisapproved";s:16:"Entry unapproved";s:15:"recordsnotsaved";s:65:"No entry was saved. Please check the format of the uploaded file.";s:12:"recordssaved";s:13:"entries saved";s:17:"removealldatatags";s:60:"Loại bỏ toàn bộ các thẻ trong cơ sở dữ liệu";s:15:"requireapproval";s:24:"Yêu cầu chấp nhận";s:20:"requireapproval_help";s:70:"A teacher has to approve entries before they’re visible to everyone.";s:8:"required";s:10:"Yêu cầu";s:15:"requiredentries";s:37:"Entries required for completion (old)";s:20:"requiredentries_help";s:419:"If set, a message is displayed stating the number of entries required for completion. Note that this setting is not connected to activity completion.

